org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.ui.liveedit

Class LiveEditDiffViewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.ui.liveedit.LiveEditDiffViewer

  • public class LiveEditDiffViewer
extends java.lang.Object
    A UI control that shows V8 update preview. It consists of function tree structure and source text viewer each for both old and new version of the script. The tree viewers are synchronized together: their selection, expansion and scroll position are synchronized.
